graph LR
    TrustyAI[TrustyAI Service Operator]

    %% External Dependencies
    TrustyAI -->|model serving| KServe[KServe v0.12.1+<br/>REQUIRED]
    TrustyAI -->|runtime platform| Kubernetes[Kubernetes v1.19+<br/>REQUIRED]
    TrustyAI -->|build toolchain| Go[Go 1.23<br/>REQUIRED]
    TrustyAI -->|job queuing| Kueue[Kueue v0.6.2<br/>OPTIONAL]
    TrustyAI -->|metrics collection| PrometheusOp[Prometheus Operator v0.64.1<br/>OPTIONAL]

    %% Internal ODH Dependencies
    TrustyAI -->|patches/watches| InferenceServices[KServe InferenceServices<br/>CRD Watch/Patch]
    TrustyAI -->|external access| Routes[OpenShift Routes<br/>CRD Create]
    TrustyAI -->|service mesh routing| VirtualService[Istio VirtualService<br/>CRD Create]
    TrustyAI -->|traffic policies| DestinationRule[Istio DestinationRule<br/>CRD Create]
    TrustyAI -.->|optional integration| ServiceMesh[Service Mesh<br/>mTLS]

    %% External Services
    TrustyAI -->|data persistence| Database[PostgreSQL/MySQL<br/>5432/3306 TCP]
    TrustyAI -->|model storage| S3[S3-compatible Storage<br/>443 HTTPS]
    TrustyAI -->|model metadata| ModelRegistry[Model Registry<br/>443 HTTPS]
    TrustyAI -->|API server| K8sAPI[Kubernetes API<br/>6443 HTTPS]

    %% Integration Points
    Dashboard[ODH Dashboard] -.->|UI management| TrustyAI
    Pipelines[Data Science Pipelines] -.->|auto evaluation| TrustyAI
    KServeInf[KServe Inference] -->|payload logging| TrustyAI
    Prometheus[Prometheus] -->|scrapes metrics| TrustyAI

    %% Component Categories
    subgraph "Required External"
        KServe
        Kubernetes
        Go
    end

    subgraph "Optional External"
        Kueue
        PrometheusOp
    end

    subgraph "ODH Integration"
        InferenceServices
        Routes
        VirtualService
        DestinationRule
        ServiceMesh
    end

    subgraph "External Services"
        Database
        S3
        ModelRegistry
        K8sAPI
    end

    subgraph "ODH Integrations (Reverse)"
        Dashboard
        Pipelines
        KServeInf
        Prometheus
    end

